A) [Option A]
B) [Option B]
C) [Option C]
D) [Option D]

What's your answer? (A, B, C, or D)"

### 2. Answer Collection and Validation

Wait for user to enter A, B, C, or D.

Accept case-insensitive answers. If invalid, prompt:
